WEBVTT

NOTE Captions for the feature / state-documentation video. Timings are approximate.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.500
Let me give you the tour. CareBase runs your whole facility from one place.

2
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:13.000
Training and credentials. Clearances and monthly exclusion screening.
Scheduling and staffing.

3
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:19.000
Incidents and investigations. Fire drills and emergency plans.
Billing and resident finances.

4
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.000
And a one-click compliance binder, ready for survey day.

5
00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:29.500
But here's where it really shines. Your state documentation.

6
00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:37.500
Take RASP assessments and support plans. Instead of wrestling with blank
forms, CareBase simply asks you questions about the resident,

7
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:43.000
and files your answers into exactly the right sections. Automatically.

8
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:49.500
When something changes, or the yearly update comes due, it's just a few clicks.

9
00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:54.000
No re-typing. No missed deadlines. No blank fields for the surveyor to find.

10
00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:01.000
That's the difference. CareBase doesn't just store your compliance —
it builds it with you, and keeps it survey-ready, every single day.
